This deployment has been trested on minikube

Prerequisite:
Running minikube or kubernetes cluster


>kubectl apply -f deployment.yaml
>kubectl apply -f loadballance.yaml

The IP address and port can be displayed with the fillowing:
>minikube service web-lb


This works for images/servers that run a task that keeps them running.
The yaml deployment files have been kept seporate to alow for further 
development and simplicity.
